Brief job description:
1. Brand protection is a certificate transferred from the seller of goods to the buyer using a smartphone application operating in the TRON blockchain.
2. Using our platform, the manufacturer of the goods registers a brand (creates an account on the TRON network)
3. Creates tokens with the description of the goods (the number of goods-tokens, wine-type goods, date of issue, additional information)
4.Exports the account to the phone, further work goes using the application.
5. At the moment, the development of the project is in the direction of creating a system of control over any product from a milk bottle to a bag of Chanel.
6. A web wallet will be added to the site and the application will be completed under IOS.
7. A product marking system has been created using the QR code.
